### Get all alerts
GET http://localhost:5000/api/alerts
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get only unacknowledged alerts
GET http://localhost:5000/api/alerts?unacknowledged=true
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Acknowledge a specific alert (replace <alert_id> with actual ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/alerts/0/acknowledge
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Clear all alerts
POST http://localhost:5000/api/alerts/clear
Content-Type: application/json

###
